metadata.name: Eye of the Valley
metadata.description:
'Eye of the Valley' by aumichrome  
2022  
9545x5966 pixels

'Eye of the Valley' was created at Moraine Lake Alberta. Captured at sunrise, it was created by combining multiple images capturing infrared and visible light. It is this artist's first infrared image minted on the blockchain.
